<bibRefCitation author="OPITZ" box="[815,965,422,444]" firstAuthor="OPITZ" pageId="9" pageNumber="136" pagination="29 - 117" refId="ref18217" refString="OPITZ W. (2017 a): Classification, Natural History, and Evolution of the Subfamily Peloniinae OPITZ (Coleoptera: Cleroidea: Cleridae). Part VII. The World Genera of Peloniinae (Coleoptera: Cleridae). Linzer biologische Beitrage 49 (1): 29 - 117." type="journal article" year="2017" yearSuffix="a">OPITZ (2017a)</bibRefCitation>
