<figureCitation box="[185,262,509,531]" captionStart="Figs 65-66" captionStartId="21.[178,218,1277,1299]" captionTargetBox="[275,995,226,1244]" captionTargetId="figure@21.[251,1018,198,1268]" captionTargetPageId="21" captionText="Figs 65-66: Elytra and epipleural margin of Amphelissus meieri. (65) Elytra. (66) Epipleuron." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3762408" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3762408/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="136">Fig. 65</figureCitation>
